esult of this work, therefore, fills the gap\nbetween first-principle studies of the $nn \\to pp\\,(ee)$ amplitude from lattice\nQCD and those from effective field theory, and can be readily employed in the\nongoing lattice-QCD studies of this process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Dec 2020 17:15:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2021 17:47:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-20"}
