ects of our system, and b) film-makers who watched footage filmed using\nLookOut.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Dec 2020 17:20:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Dec 2020 22:04:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 30 Apr 2022 21:38:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-03"}
