l attacks is neither readily available nor\nstraightforward to achieve since surrogate models for wireless applications may\nsignificantly differ from the target model depending on channel effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Dec 2020 18:46:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Mar 2021 00:01:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-10"}
