h are graph\nclasses that are defined by purely combinatorial notions and properly contain\ngraph classes with some natural topological and geometric flavours.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Dec 2020 07:29:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Dec 2020 08:28:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 21 May 2021 20:28:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-25"}
