 the energy spectrum. A cut-based\nstrategy and a multivariate approach indicated a rate, attributed to the\nintrinsic radioactivity of the crystal, of $\\sim$1 count/day/kg/keV in the\n[5-20] keV region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Dec 2020 14:13:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Apr 2021 08:49:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-13"}
